articles.title: SpaceX will launch Europe's Hera asteroid probe on Oct. 7: Watch it live - Space.com
articles.description: Liftoff is scheduled for Monday (Oct. 7) at 10:52 a.m. EDT (1452 GMT).
articles.content:
SpaceX will launch Europe's Hera spacecraft toward the asteroid Dimorphos for a post-impact evaluation on Monday (Oct. 7), and you can watch the liftoff live.
